<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rainie越南语教室 - 跟YouTube明星学越南语</title>
    <style>
        /* 柔和配色方案 */
        :root {
            --cream: #F5F3E7;
            --sage: #B5C2B7;
            --clay: #D4A373;
            --text: #4A4A48;
        }

        body {
            background: var(--cream);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* 动态导航栏 */
        .navbar {
            background: rgba(245, 243, 231, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 1rem 5%;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .navbar.scrolled {
            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        /* 动态按钮特效 */
        .cta-btn {
            background: var(--clay);
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .cta-btn::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            left: -100%;
            top: 0;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .cta-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(212,163,115,0.3);
        }

        .cta-btn:hover::after {
            left: 100%;
        }

        /* 自我介绍模块 */
        .bio-section {
            padding: 6rem 5%;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .bio-photo {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        /* 电子书宣传 */
        .ebook-banner {
            background: var(--sage);
            padding: 4rem 5%;
            text-align: center;
            clip-path: polygon(0 10%, 100% 0, 100% 90%, 0 100%);
            margin: 5rem 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- 导航栏 -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">Rainie越南语</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#bio">教师简介</a>
            <a href="#courses">课程体系</a>
            <a href="#ebook">教材订购</a>
            <a href="#contact">联系我们</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- 自我介绍 -->
    <section class="bio-section" id="bio">
        <img src="rainie-profile.jpg" alt="Rainie老师专业形象照" class="bio-photo">
        <div>
            <h1>你好，我是Rainie老师！</h1>
            <p>✦ 越南河内大学语言学硕士 | 中文双语教学专家 ✦</p>
            <p>拥有8年跨境语言教学经验，YouTube频道累计观看超2000万次。我的教学方法融合现代语言习得理论与越南传统文化，独创"情景式母语浸入法"，帮助3000+中文母语者实现：</p>
            <ul>
                <li>3个月掌握日常会话核心框架</li>
                <li>6个月达到商务沟通水平</li>
                <li>1年突破C1高级越南语认证</li>
            </ul>
            <p>教学特色：<br>
            通过影视剧台词解析+真实场景模拟，破解中文母语者特有的发音难点。独创"越南语声调记忆图谱"，帮助学员精准掌握6大声调系统。</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 电子书宣传 -->
    <section class="ebook-banner" id="ebook">
        <h2>《越南语核心1000句》电子版</h2>
        <p>精选20个生活场景 × 50个商务情境 × 30个文化专题<br>
        包含：<br>
        ✅ 逐句拼音标注 & 声调示意图<br>
        ✅ 情境对话MP3下载（含慢速/常速双版本）<br>
        ✅ 独家"易错点对照表"</p>
        <a href="#" class="cta-btn">立即订购电子书</a>
        <p style="margin-top:1rem;"><small>※ 订购后请联系YouTube频道客服获取下载链接</small></p>
    </section>

    <!-- 最新视频 -->
    <section style="padding:6rem 5%">
        <h2>最新教学视频</h2>
        <div style="max-width:800px; margin:2rem auto;">
            <div style="position:relative; padding-bottom:56.25%; height:0;">
                <iframe 
                    src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0KC0yjZofEU" 
                    style="position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%;"
                    frameborder="0"
                    allowfullscreen>
                </iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 联系方式 -->
    <footer style="background:var(--text); color:white; padding:4rem 5%; text-align:center;" id="contact">
        <h3>获取专属学习方案</h3>
        <p>通过以下方式联系我们：</p>
        <div style="margin:2rem 0;">
            <a href="https://youtube.com/你的频道链接" 
               style="color:var(--clay); text-decoration:none;"
               target="_blank">
               YouTube频道私信咨询
            </a>
        </div>
        <p>服务时间：周一至周五 09:00-18:00 (GMT+8)</p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // 导航栏滚动特效
        window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
            const navbar = document.querySelector('.navbar');
            if(window.scrollY > 50) {
                navbar.classList.add('scrolled');
            } else {
                navbar.classList.remove('scrolled');
            }
        });

        // 动态加载特效
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            const elements = document.querySelectorAll('.bio-section, .ebook-banner');
            elements.forEach(el => {
                el.style.opacity = '0';
                el.style.transform = 'translateY(30px)';
                
                const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
                    entries.forEach(entry => {
                        if(entry.isIntersecting) {
                            entry.target.style.opacity = '1';
                            entry.target.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';
                            entry.target.style.transition = 'all 0.6s ease-out';
                        }
                    });
                });
                
                observer.observe(el);
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
